messages.content: whast is our annual revenue for 2024?
Our annual revenue for 2024 is $8.5 Million, representing a 63% year-over-year growth from the $5.2 Million in revenue generated in 2023.
who is the CEO and what is the background?
Sarah Johnson is the Chief Executive Officer (CEO), with a background as the former VP of Engineering at Google Cloud for 8 years.
Our lead investor is Andreessen Horowitz (a16z), with Sequoia Capital also participating in the funding rounds.

Our Q1 goals for Marketing Initiatives include launching a new AI Revolution Campaign, creating and publishing 50 blog posts and 10 whitepapers, sponsoring 3 major tech conferences, hosting weekly product demonstrations through a webinar series, partnering with 10 tech influencers, and generating 5,000 new leads.
